Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:53.70,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(900,0)}QUARTO NÍVEL - CAMPO DE GIRASSÓIS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}E então?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,O chão deste platô ondula \Ncomo se fosse uma bandeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Que desajeitado!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você não rasteja no chão,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,soldadinho de brinquedo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:08.73,Title,,0,0,240,,{\fad(800,800)}Cabbage e Romeo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Já entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo está conectado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,O soldadinho de brinquedo que chorava\N e gritava como um idiota naquele dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...era você, não era?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:27.77,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1300)}Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}O marido da falecida Scarlett \Ne o pai de Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Você e eu estamos unidos \Npelo destino, Kyros.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,É por isso que eu vim até aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bom movimento!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas esta capa é de ferro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Tenha cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Vipera Glaive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também vou lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Lute, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu quero ver Kyros perder \Nsua esposa e sua filha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me protegê-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso também é por Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me compensar você por\N ter te ensinado a lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vivi envergonhado \Npor ter feito isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que voltei a ser humano,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,não vou permitir que\N minha filha empunhe uma espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I-Isso é terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:22.65,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(496,0)}NÍVEL 2 DO PLATÔ REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Derrotaram Lao G-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Que poder destrutivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu já ouvi esse nome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A Armada Happou do País de Ka, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou esquecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Nunca se sabe quem pode \Nse tornar nosso inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Velho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, velho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Não morra, velho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, vou reservar dois salões\N para cerimônias, querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Dois salões para cerimônias?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Querido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Para o nosso casamento...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...e para o funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não mate as pessoas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.14,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Não mate as pessoas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.36,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(510,0)}NÍVEL 3 DO PLATÔ REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você não para de se mover \Nfurtivamente de um lado para o outro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos lutar, Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tente a sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas o que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me digam que Gladius-sama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,O chão inteiro está se expandindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Você sabe o que vai acontecer, não sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Você estava preparando isso \Nhá um tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é perigoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.53,Main,,0,0,0,,O chão vai explodir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe entrar na sua barreira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu desativar, Robin-senpai \Ne eu estaremos em perigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso, os inimigos também entrariam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, abra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou seu aliado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Assim, nós também...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês são os melhores dos melhores, não são?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Abra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Punk Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...Fest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Adeus, Cavendish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você estivesse lá fora, \Nteria morrido na hora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você ia me deixar entrar, \Ndevia ter feito isso antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Que susto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.47,Main,,0,0,0,,O que há de errado com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,É assim que você agradece quem te salvou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas eu estive te protegendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também deve me agradecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu preciso continuar atacando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe sair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu acabei de te deixar entrar\N e já quer sair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que entrou, fique \Num pouco mais de tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu egoísta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é um hotel ou o quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Se defenda e depois ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,É óbvio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou mais te deixar entrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe entrar quando eu estiver em apuros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu inútil inflexível!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Você vai me pagar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim! Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Que alívio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Estou indo, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Fique segura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin, sua mulher incômoda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar que incomode\N os oficiais supremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Catapult Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Barreira-habilidade: Raquete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda está vivo, hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá em frente, vá em frente, Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Galo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ele piscou para mim, foi uma piscadela!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Eu agradeço muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Foi um "muito bem, galo-kun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:36.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Um "você pode se tornar\N meu escravo se quiser"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não, não, que presunçoso, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Isso é pedir demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...estou queimando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Você estava na barreira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pena, Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Biken: Blue...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Bracchium...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.78,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Barrier Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,A barreira está vindo atrás de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Vale a pena arriscar a vida\N de um homem por sua piscadela!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também estou aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas há uma razão pela qual\N não posso parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Qual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque eu sinto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...que estou queimando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me importo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Você ainda não terminou de\N organizar o segundo nível?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou quase terminando aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Venha ajudar no terceiro nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin está tentando subir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou ocupado com esses dois idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu te disse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...para não se distrair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Caramba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é persistente, braços longos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu já achava que seu corpo\N parecia muito estranho...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...por causa desses ombros altos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem um buraco no estômago,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,por que não morre logo,\N campeão dos lutadores?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Tenho um dever a cumprir\N neste mundo dos homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Seria uma vergonha para\N aqueles que foram derrotados!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não parece algo que você diria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você tivesse fingido de morto,\N eu teria poupado sua vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,De que adianta continuar se levantando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Talvez sirva para\N ganhar algum tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Até que Chapéu de Palha\N derrote Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,não vamos deixar que vocês\N atrapalhem o caminho dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é o que todos nós faremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Neste mundo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:16.40,Main,,0,0,0,,ninguém pode vencer sozinho, moleque!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Então querem vencer se sacrificando, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é coisa de escória!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Os fortes não precisam de compaixão!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também não sou um humano comum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}Nunca subestime a linhagem\N dos peixes de briga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.10,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1095,460)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(300,300)}NÍVEL 3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Fique aí embaixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,É perigoso aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem um inimigo problemático!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não parece algo que você diria,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ninguém é problema para nós\N quando lutamos juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Dellinger...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquele maldito moleque com chifres...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...e os outros soldados inimigos...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.50,Main,,0,0,0,,...foram derrotados!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Do outro lado da barreira,\N tem um cara assustador!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Q-Quem é ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele parece aquele maldito Cabbage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,mas o rosto dele é completamente diferente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...exatamente o que aconteceu\N no Bloco D do coliseu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Incrível!{665}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(0,478)}Todos foram derrubados!{665}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi ele quem fez isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa roupa é definitivamente\N a do Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas o rosto dele parece\N o de outro-dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O que-vendish é ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Q-Que susto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é tão rápido que não pude vê-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não importa o quão rápido você seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,É inútil contra minha habilidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está pensando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você levar as brincadeiras\N longe demais...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Para quem você está olhando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça besteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vá atrás da Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Diante de mim, a velocidade não adianta nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem uma aparência maligna,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Cabbage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Posso ajudar em algo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou preocupada com a Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Preciso me apressar para subir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela o deteve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Dobin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.46,Secondary,,0,0,0,,(Robin-senpai).
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Alguém como eu tentar protegê-la,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:31.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,como eu pensava, é ser\N muito presunçoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere, Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não te dei permissão para aparecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Quase te cortei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Então esse era o famoso Hakuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonambulismo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,É um incômodo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele só fica cortando pessoas\N indiscriminadamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Não só seus braços e pernas,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,eu vou despedaçar todo\N o seu corpo, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou cortar tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Desapareça, Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vai assumir o controle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Durma, Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não entende o que\N essa luta significa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu é que vou lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero cortar tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Não adianta nada\N se não for eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me importo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou mostrar um mar de sangue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,É como se duas pessoas\N estivessem conversando!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele tem dupla personalidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu, eu, eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu, eu, eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.06,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora estão meio a meio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca, Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Cavendish sou só eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Há pouco estavam\N meio a meio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Já estou bem, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Você poderia me soltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Você quer que eu confie em você\N depois do que eu vi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou acabar com isso agora\N que estão ocupados.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou mandá-los voar\N junto com esse muro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vão apenas voar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Não pensem que sairão ilesos disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquele desgraçado...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:14.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele quer explodir o muro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Devemos descer, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Se algo acontecer com a Rebecca\N enquanto eu fizer isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar que você machuque\N a Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Boa decisão.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Se me derrotar, você pode\N evitar que o muro exploda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Punk Hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou dormente!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses fios são agulhas envenenadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou usuário da Pamu Pamu no Mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ou seja, sou um homem\N explosivo da cabeça aos pés.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você tentar algo comigo,\N meu corpo explodirá...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...e dezenas de agulhas envenenadas,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,como as que acabei de lançar em você,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,vão atravessar os corpos\N daqueles dois lá em cima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas se não me derrotar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,não poderá evitar que o muro exploda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,E então? O que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro que a força da minha explosão\N é tão poderosa que você não sobreviverá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que, de qualquer forma,\N a Robin-senpai acabará machucada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Você entende rápido, Bartolomeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pense, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:50.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Qual é a minha prioridade agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Minha prioridade é, claro,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,o corpo da Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Para impedir a explosão do muro,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:01.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,225)}preciso derrotar esse ouriço,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:07.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,348)}mas, então, uma grande quantidade\N de agulhas envenenadas atingiria a Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O que eu faço?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pense, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,É isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem alguém dispensável\N ao lado da Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou acabar com esse ouriço,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,então você protege a Robin-senpai\N das agulhas envenenadas usando seu corpo como escudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca, galo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,O assustador voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele continua sendo um inútil\N num momento crucial como este!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,A Robin-senpai está em perigo\N por todos os lados!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,O que eu faço?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Já sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Você vai me atacar, Bartolomeo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:16.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Só posso ter uma barreira por vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Essa é minha fraqueza, mas não importa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:25.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:29.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Se assim eu puder salvar você,\N não hesitarei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Barrier Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Estoure o quanto quiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos dentro da barreira invencível!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse idiota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Galo-kun, você...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está disposto a se sacrificar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Fashion Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Galo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:11.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Você merece, ouriço!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:16.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Assim poderei evitar que o muro exploda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:19.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pude proteger a Robin-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pena, estúpido.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Você errou por alguns centímetros...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você atingiu não foi minha garganta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi meu ombro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:47.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não acertei o ponto vital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:48.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Como ele estava em forma de bola,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:51.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,não sabia se era o ombro ou a garganta...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:53.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:56.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também é um usuário de Akuma no Mi,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:58.04,Main,,0,0,0,,então você deve saber, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:01.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Enquanto eu não perder a consciência,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,a explosão do muro não vai parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Veja bem como seus amigos desaparecem!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:14.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:17.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Que estúpido eu sou!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin, sinto muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Já tenho o Hakuba sob controle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:30.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ainda resta metade do Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Me solte!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.18,0:24:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos fugir para o campo de girassóis\N com a velocidade do Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.84,0:24:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou usar a habilidade do Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos outra alternativa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Tire essas mãos de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Confie em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.98,0:24:47.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Qual dos dois é ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos tempo para dúvidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.08,0:24:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.14,0:24:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.21,0:24:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Punk Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,...Super Arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.82,0:25:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.48,0:25:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Que barreira boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.56,0:25:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sobrou nada deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.75,0:25:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.26,0:25:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você me parou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.01,0:25:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,É o seu corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.92,0:25:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, por que você...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.10,0:25:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...não ouve o que eu digo de vez em quando?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.82,0:25:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Cien Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.12,0:25:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.86,0:25:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Você parou a espada do Hakuba\N por mim, não foi, Cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.60,0:26:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pessoa complexa.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.83,0:26:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Como eles conseguiram escapar\N dessa explosão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.82,0:26:15.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ao contrário dele,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:18.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,eu não valho nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.60,0:26:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Homage Shinken!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.96,0:26:26.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.72,0:26:29.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ainda preciso melhorar muito\N mais minhas habilidades,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.76,0:26:32.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,mas vou ficar cada vez mais forte...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.70,0:26:34.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Bari Bari no...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.66,0:26:42.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,E um dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.62,0:26:48.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...vou me tornar um homem\N que possa realmente te ajudar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.62,0:27:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mal consegui vencer \Ncom o poder do meu senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não quero mais fazer equipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.78,0:27:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...com alguém tão problemático quanto ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:28.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,390)\fad(300,300)}QUARTO NÍVEL\NCAMPO DE GIRASSÓIS
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.20,0:27:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muito barulho lá embaixo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.28,0:27:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Em um campo de batalha \Ntão instável quanto este,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.67,0:27:40.03,Main,,0,0,0,,até os gladiadores do \Ncoliseu vacilam e caem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.72,0:27:44.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Vipera Glaive!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.60,0:27:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Fuja, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.28,0:27:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não pode se defender desse ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Flores borboleta multicoloridas \Nque repelem ataques!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Mil Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.52,0:27:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Kochouran!{orquídea borboleta}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.69,0:28:01.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.26,0:28:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa mulher...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.82,0:28:04.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Robiland!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.78,0:28:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Você cumpriu sua missão, Rebecca.
